Title: 
PO Approved!

Body:
<table width="95%" height="416" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
  <tr>
    <td  valign="top" height="416"><span class="textblack"><br>
      <br>
      </span>Dear ${user.name} (${role}),
      <p>This is to notify you that the following PO you created has been Approved.</p>
      <table width="90%"  border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="1" bgcolor="#666666">
        <tr bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
          <td><span class="bold">PO No.</span></td>
          <td><span class="bold">PO Title</span></td>
          <td><span class="bold">Supplier Name</span></td>
          <td><span class="bold"><span class="textblack">Purchase Category</span></span></td>
          <td><span class="bold"><span class="textblack">Purchase Currency</span></span></td>
          <td><span class="bold">Purchase Amount</span></td>
          <td><span class="bold">Base Currency</span></td>
          <td><span class="bold">Base Amount</span></td>
          <td><span class="bold">Creator</span></td>
          <td><span class="bold">Create Date</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
          <td><div align="left"><span class="textblack">${po.id}</span></div></td>
          <td><div align="left"><span class="textblack">${po.title}</span></div></td>
          <td><div align="left"><span class="textblack">${po.supplier.name}</span></div></td>
          <td><div align="left"><span class="textblack">${po.subCategory.description}</span></div></td>
          <td><div align="left"><span class="textblack">${po.exchangeRate.currency.name}</span></div></td>
          <td><div align="left"><span class="textblack">${po.amount}</span></div></td>
          <td><div align="left"><span class="textblack">${po.baseCurrency.name}</span></div></td>
          <td><div align="left"><span class="textblack">${po.baseCurrencyAmount}</span></div></td>
          <td><div align="left"><span class="textblack">${po.purchaser.name}</span></div></td>
          <td><div align="left"><span class="textblack">$dateTool.format('yyyy/MM/dd', $po.createDate)</span></div></td>
        </tr>
      </table>      <p>&nbsp;</p>
      <p>Please use your web browser to go to:<br>
      ${visitUrl} visit our system.</p>
      <p>${regardWords}<br>
      ${signature}</p>
      <p></p>
    <p></p></td>
  </tr>
</table>